_sText:
This is a re skin of the original bhop_treehouse. I've been wanting to make this for awhile now but I never got around to it. I've had a lot of free time the past few days so decided I would just get it out of the way. 

Although I was tempted to change the gameplay in some areas in the end I decided not to so it would still have that classic feel to it. Times on this and the original should be basically interchangeable. 

I did make a little bonus just for the revamp though.

This will probably be my last bhop map for awhile
